Author: phmwls
Text: I told my brother and sister about it like “omg haha this subreddit is funny (the ed memes one) and helps me cope bc of my “past” so I can look back and grow from it - kinda like dark humor haha.” They hate it but still laugh at the memes and think it’s benign. If they find my phone, I just hope they don’t know this app well enough to look at my post and comment history. For the record, I do think it helps me and makes me feel like I’m not alone, but the ideas and things I read thooooo. Sometimes it’s the only interaction I have in a day and it gets so normalized that I sometimes talk about it in public in a jokey way and people are like 😶
